### рџџЎ P4.2 вЂ” Dry-run (view last results without running)
**Why medium:** Lets operators review the most recent health status without triggering a new check run.
**Status: вњ… DONE (via History tab)** вЂ” The History tab (P3.2) already delivers this functionality: `/api/history` serves cached run summaries, `/api/history/{run_id}` fetches full details from the bastion DB via SSH, and the Refresh button re-syncs from all bastions. Users can view any past run's results without triggering a new check.

**Remaining UX polish (optional):**
- A dedicated "Dry Run" one-click button that auto-loads the most recent run
